Package org.jclouds.ec2.features

Interface Summary
AMIApi Provides access to AMI Services.
AvailabilityZoneAndRegionApi Provides access to EC2 Availability Zones and Regions via their REST API.
ElasticBlockStoreApi Provides access to EC2 Elastic Block Store services via their REST API.
ElasticIPAddressApi Provides access to EC2 Elastic IP Addresses via REST API.
InstanceApi Provides access to EC2 Instance Services via their REST API.
KeyPairApi Provides access to EC2 via their REST API.
SecurityGroupApi Provides access to EC2 via their REST API.
SubnetApi Provides access to Amazon EC2 via the Query API

TagApi Provides access to Amazon EC2 via the Query API

WindowsApi Provides access to EC2 Windows Features via the Query API
